snippet.title: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban | PS2/Xbox/GC/GBA/PC | 2004 | V.G. UK Teaser | LQ/OGR
snippet.description:
UK Teaser for the Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban video game, based on the book and the 2004 movie of the same name.

Published in the United Kingdom by EA in 2004 for PlayStation 2, Xbox, Nintendo GameCube, Game Boy Advance, and Windows
PlayStation 2, Xbox, and Nintendo GameCube versions developed by EA UK
Game Boy Advance version developed by Griptonite
Windows version developed by KnowWonder

Teaser in low quality. Original resolution.
